{"tid":839952,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東方日報 不用種罌粟 也可製鴉片？","createTime":"2018-09-28T10:10:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-28T10:17:04.000Z","uid":57214,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"534dab21e69c3210672ca7342753fcfa8bc842b1","tid":839952,"uid":57214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T10:10:43.000Z","msg":"罌粟目前是製造嗎啡和海洛英等鴉片類藥物的唯一來源，惟加拿大協和大學宣布研發了一種基因改造酵母，能把糖分轉化成這些藥物的分子，未來或不用再種植罌粟，亦能低成本生產藥物。<br />\n<br />\n該種基因改造酵母與目前酒類製造過程中的酵母類似，研究人員利用它來提取鎮痛劑如可待因、蒂巴因和嗎啡的分子。由於現時製造鴉片類藥物，主要是從罌粟膠汁中提取可待因和蒂巴因，是次研究或意味，未來生產或不須種植罌粟，也能製造鴉片類藥物，甚至扭轉全球毒品的貿易。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20150518/mobile/odn-20150518-0518_00180_031.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20150518%2Fmobile%2Fodn-20150518-0518_00180_031.html&d=TpGw%2FtpkxdTkwnVWdDB6pTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=cb6741e9\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20150518/mobile/odn-20150518-0518_00180_031.html</a>"},{"pid":"4a52cd7888d4f2e7ff2848142945e26dd228c304","tid":839952,"uid":34010,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T10:15:59.000Z","msg":"東方真係勁，咁都識 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"669c0d9994e507c144aef622a3862e1a9a90130d","tid":839952,"uid":78533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T10:17:04.000Z","msg":"白粉報<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}